(1322, 255, 'description', 'Deltex cables with their tension memory present special characteristic in mainting the initial constant tension. Its component based on <strong>polyester and carbon monofilament fibre</strong> secure high resistance under extreme conditions. These cables upgrade the normal steel cables.\r\n\r\n-Unique tension memory : Deltex may have a wider angle but<strong> remains</strong><strong> at its initial tension</strong> (does not need maintenance for re-tension which maybe dangerous).\r\n\r\n- Security : The technology makes an <strong>ELECTRICAL CONDUCTION OFF the cable</strong> (there is <strong>no lighting attraction</strong>) and the rupture resistance is very high : 65 kgF/mm2.\r\n\r\n- Specially very light cable (density of 1,40kg/dm3): Deltex is <strong>4 times lighter</strong> as the steel cable makes easier installation and get a higher resistance (ex: weight comparison between Deltex cable and steel cable on a 500 meters distance).\r\n\r\n- Excellent performance under difficult climate conditions: <strong>No oxidation</strong>, it does not loose its tension (Deltex is thermo-retractable).\r\n\r\n- Higher shelf life : Thanks to its special pulley, Deltex cable allows far <strong>more descents</strong>.\r\n\r\n- High quality accessories development : Thanks to its knowledge in this sector, Deltex offers special steel pulleys with doble ball bearings for a <strong>better feeling</strong>. Canopy with Deltex is completely <strong>SILENT</strong>.\r\n\r\n- Easy to install, easy to maintain: With Deltex clips, like light cones or special grips, the <strong>installation is easy and fast</strong>, same for structure <strong>maintenance</strong>. This is confirmed by all fitters.'),
(1323, 255, '_description', 'field_562d2607279ba'),
